TALK Narrator Using an item you have picked up is simple
TALK Narrator Open your inventory (z) and use the arrow keys to highlight the bomb
TALK Narrator Now press Attack (left ctrl) or Use Item (a) to select it
TALK Narrator Now close the inventory (z)
TALK Narrator You can now use the item by pressing Use Item (a)
TALK Narrator Try it with the bomb, but make sure you stand well back!
TALK Narrator While you are in the inventory screen, the action is paused so you can take your time
TALK Narrator Some items, such as health potions and weapons can be used in the inventory screen, so there is no need to exit the inventory
